comments: Trent Jr. (TOR) brings his hand toward LaVine's (CHI) side and marginal contact occurs during LaVine's  drive.
Beverley (CHI) and Anunoby (TOR) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in DeRozan's (CHI) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Barnes (TOR) extends his arm and marginal contact occurs to Beverley's (CHI) arm as they pursue the loose ball.
Barnes (TOR) establishes himself in LaVine's (CHI) path and does not deliver contact.
Vucevic (CHI) and Siakam (TOR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs as Siakam attempts to gather the pass in the lane.
Vucevic (CHI) briefly places his hand to Siakam's (TOR) arm underneath the basket and slides his hand off during rebounding.
Beverley (CHI) and Anunoby (TOR) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Beverley (CHI) and Anunoby (TOR) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Caruso (CHI) establishes himself in Anunoby's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Anunoby (TOR) briefly brings his arm to DeRozan's (CHI) front and marginal contact occurs during his drive before correcting.
Barnes (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Trent Jr. (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Caruso (CHI) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Caruso (CHI) is moving alongside VanVleet's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during VanVleet's drive.
Trent Jr. (TOR) places a steady hand to LaVine's (CHI) front during his drive and releases away without applying force.
After the release of Trent Jr.'s (TOR) shot attempt, Trent Jr. goes to the floor and in doing so trips LaVine (CHI) and affects his SQBR following his defensive contest.
After initially absorbing the contact to his front Anunoby (TOR) lifts his forearm arm upward and delivers contact to DeRozan (CHI) which affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams (CHI) initiates contact with Siakam's (TOR) arm and affects Siakam's SQBR.
Beverley (CHI) and VanVleet (TOR) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Caruso (CHI) briefly grasps Trent Jr.'s (TOR) arm off ball and immediately slides his hand off as he gathers the inbound pass.
Caruso (CHI) commits a take foul on Trent Jr. (TOR).
Beverley (CHI) inbounds the ball within 5 seconds.
Siakam (TOR) grasps and then releases Vucevic's (CHI) jersey off-ball.
Anunoby (TOR) grasps and releases DeRozan's (CHI) jersey off-ball.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in Siakam's (TOR) path and does not deliver contact.
Barnes (TOR) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
DeRozan (CHI) commits a take foul on Anunoby (TOR).
DeRozan (CHI) brushes Barnes' (TOR) arm and marginal contact occurs during Barnes' shot attempt near the rim.
Barnes (TOR) blocks the shot attempt after the ball reaches its apex and starts its downward trajectory.
Beverley (CHI) places two steady hands to VanVleet's (TOR) body before correcting.
